rComments: If you get the textbook you don't really need to go to class. I only went to lectures where the stuff being covered wasn't in the textbook (he indicates those classes on the syllabus) and did great. He is a great prof and if it wasn't an 8:30am class I probably would've gone more often. He's funny and engaging and exams are fair ( 2 MT 1 Final)

Bon prof, bien pour sa 1e année d'enseignement. Il est bizarre et un peu déplacé, mais drôle. Ses exams sont bien, mais la formulation de ses questions porte à confusion. Prêt à aider en dehors de la classe, gentil, mais il est confus dans ses explications. Le livre est pas nécessaire. Il donne des réponses à des questions d'exam en classe parfois.

He's a great prof. Weekly online quizzes that are just basically grade boosters. He's an easy grade and the material is fairly easy. Attending isn't mandatory but it might help. Didn't buy the textbook and still did well so don't waste your money. He's a really chill and funny prof too so his class was always enjoyable to attend!
